Privacy Policy for SVCE Locator App

Last updated: October 27, 2025

Thank you for using SVCE Locator, developed by Rajat Dashore ("we", "our", or "us").
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application SVCE Locator (‚ÄúApp‚Äù).

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:

a. Personal Information

Email address ‚Äî when you log in or sign up using our authentication system (Firebase Authentication).

Name and profile details ‚Äî if you choose to provide them in your profile.

b. Location Information

We may collect real-time location data (via Google Maps API) to help locate your position inside or near the SVCE campus.

Location is only collected with your permission and used to display or navigate the campus map.

c. Device Information

We may automatically collect information such as device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers for app performance and analytics.

d. Usage Data

Information about how you use the app, such as visited screens, errors, and feature interactions, may be collected through Firebase Analytics to improve user experience.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:

Provide and improve app functionality.

Authenticate users securely.

Display accurate maps and navigation.

Communicate updates or important notices.

Analyze app performance and fix bugs.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell or rent your personal data to anyone.
We may share data only with:

Firebase (Google LLC) for authentication, analytics, and database storage.

Google Maps Platform for map and location services.

All third-party services comply with their respective privacy policies (Google Privacy Policy: https://policies.google.com/privacy
).

4. Data Security

We use industry-standard encryption and Firebase security rules to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.

5. Data Retention

We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to provide our services.
If you delete your account, your information will be permanently removed from our systems within a reasonable period.

6. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access, update, or delete your personal information.

Withdraw location permission at any time via your device settings.

Contact us for data-related queries.

7. Children‚Äôs Privacy

Our app is intended for use by students and individuals aged 13 and above.
We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13.

8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically.
Any updates will be reflected here with a new ‚ÄúLast updated‚Äù date.

